channel.desc: Noah Cappe is in carnivore mode for the San Angelo Stock Show and Rodeo in Texas; From the Southwest Dog to the Show Hog, no one goes home hungry; a steak out in the form of the Spud Steak Sandwich; a midway mashup, the Apple Cheesecake Quesadilla.
